This paper is about information retrieval (IR) and the development of a self-index based retrieval system. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also discusses techniques for optimizing the ranking time, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures) or cs.DB (Databases). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of TFxIDF and BM25, which are common IR relevance measures, indicating that it could also fit into cs.DL (Digital Libraries) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
